title: Wild Personalized Return Address Labels- Set of 144, Large Self-Adhesive, Flat-Sheet Labels (2 Designs) By Colorful Images
features: Add a touch of personality to all of your stationery and cards with these Personalized Address Labels.
144 custom labels on flat sheets; label size 1 1/8" x 2 1/4"
Self-adhesive backing for quick, easy application and superior hold
Use the'Customize Now'button to add label text; Specify block or script and 1st line of personalization, up to 35 characters and 2nd line of personalization, up to 50 characters.
Colorful Image Address Labels are printed in the USA! **Please Note: We are Unable to Print Foreign Characters at This Time.
description: Like illustrations from a childhood book, jungle animal friends temp imaginations to soar to wondrous destinations. Colorful set includes 144 self-adhesive Deluxe-style personalized labels, each measuring 1 1/8" x 2 1/4". We'll print them with the name and address, message, or information you choose. Specify block or script and 1st line of personalization, up to 35 characters and 2nd line of personalization, up to 50 characters.
